description:
Hello, It's Agatha! 😊

COLLABS AND PR: agathaclmn@gmail.com

GREEN MAKEUP TUTORIAL

In today's video, I'm going to do another quick makeup tutorial! This the green eyeshadow makeup tutorial. I'm not a big fan of the color but I love how this look turned out! I've been playing with colorful eyeshadows lately and I came up with this makeup look. Let me know if you want more videos like this 🥰

Like and subscribe for more videos!! Thanks for watching and see you on my next video :)

Products used:
FACE:
Luxe Organix Ultimate Defense Tinted Sunscreen in warm
Loreal Infallible Full Wear Concealer in Cashmere
Luxe Organix x Anne Clutz Beauty Mist
Vice Cosmetics Duo-Finish Foundation in Putinamez
EB Advance Face Trio in Fig
Vice Cosmetics Awra Blush in Title

EYES:
Detail Cosmetics SuperFine Liner in Mocha
Strokes Beauty Lab Microblade Pen Perfector in Graphite
Vice Cosmetics Gandoll Volumizing Brow Gel in Light Brown
Beauty Glazed Color Board Eyeshadow Palette
Detail Cosmetics Matte Eyeliner 

LIPS:
Vice Cosmetics X Anne Clutz Gel Liner in Soft Lang Brown
Detail Cosmetics Powder Pout in Ry Velasco


If you have suggestions, please leave them below and I would love to do them soon (try ko talaga promise)
